            "id": 6008525,
            "title": "GIS-KY 5月營收65.1億元雙增 Q2起營運回穩",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>GIS-KY(業成)(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6456:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6456\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6456-TW</a>) 今 (5) 日公告 5 月營收為 65.1 億元，呈年月雙增；累計前 5 月營收 276.3 億元，較去年同期成長 7.6%；GIS 日前指出，今年第二季開始，營運將逐步回穩，新事業營收貢獻將逾 2 成。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008525%2Fl%2Ff088c69aa3322ba57a473ba6fbebf3a9.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008525%2Fl%2Ff088c69aa3322ba57a473ba6fbebf3a9.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008525%2Fl%2Ff088c69aa3322ba57a473ba6fbebf3a9.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008525%2Fl%2Ff088c69aa3322ba57a473ba6fbebf3a9.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008525%2Fl%2Ff088c69aa3322ba57a473ba6fbebf3a9.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008525%2Fl%2Ff088c69aa3322ba57a473ba6fbebf3a9.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008525%2Fl%2Ff088c69aa3322ba57a473ba6fbebf3a9.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008525%2Fl%2Ff088c69aa3322ba57a473ba6fbebf3a9.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008525%2Fl%2Ff088c69aa3322ba57a473ba6fbebf3a9.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008525%2Fl%2Ff088c69aa3322ba57a473ba6fbebf3a9.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008525%2Fl%2Ff088c69aa3322ba57a473ba6fbebf3a9.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008525%2Fl%2Ff088c69aa3322ba57a473ba6fbebf3a9.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008525%2Fl%2Ff088c69aa3322ba57a473ba6fbebf3a9.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008525%2Fl%2Ff088c69aa3322ba57a473ba6fbebf3a9.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008525%2Fl%2Ff088c69aa3322ba57a473ba6fbebf3a9.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008525%2Fl%2Ff088c69aa3322ba57a473ba6fbebf3a9.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6008525%2Fl%2Ff088c69aa3322ba57a473ba6fbebf3a9.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">GIS-KY 5月營收65.1億元年月雙增 車用、感測新事業持續成長。(圖：shutterstock)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>GIS-KY5 月營收 65.1 億元，月增率 9.57%，年增率 30.30%，累計前 5 月營收 276.3 億元，較去年同期成長 7.6%</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>GIS-KY 日前表示，第一季雖然表現較差，但第二季開始，營運將逐步回穩，約於去年持平；而近年積極布局的指紋辨識、車載應用等新事業，今年看好營收貢獻將逾 2 成。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
